@baseUrl = http://localhost:5203
@matchId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Criar partida
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "player1Name": "Alice",
  "player2Name": "Bob"
}

###

### Listar histórico de partidas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/matches
Accept: application/json

###

### Registrar jogada (Player: 0 = X, 1 = O | Position: 0-8)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/matches/{{matchId}}/moves
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matchId": "{{matchId}}",
  "player": 0,
  "position": 4,
  "moveOrder": 1
}

###

### Finalizar partida (board: array de 9 posições, null = vazio)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/matches/{{matchId}}/finish
Content-Type: application/json

["X", null, null,
 null, "X", null,
 null, null, "X"]

###
